Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:04.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This is goodbye, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:32.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,FIN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This movie always tugs at my heartstrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:49.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Misuzu Shirakawa (58)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:49.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's an old movie, but I hope you youngsters enjoyed it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:58.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Should we let them take a look around the second floor too, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:01:00.66,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kyōsuke Shirakawa (23)\NMisuzu's Son
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:00.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We have displays full of objects used in her movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, we'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:20.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only the light of deductions can tear apart black shadows and deep darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:22.15,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A fire breaks out at a movie star's mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:24.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and a picture hides a surprising secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:26.53,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:27.91,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:30.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All these movies take me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a little Misuzu Shirakawa museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're making me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My late husband collected these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room holds clothes and props from that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Mother's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We put valuable and sentimental objects inside this glass case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are these real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misuzu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wouldn't exhibit imitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that also genuine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:50.72,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Chiharu Shirakawa (22)\NMisuzu's Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be a shame to always keep it locked inside the glass case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The picture was used in the movie "A Day Off at the Deer Cry Pavilion".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:04:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since the finished picture didn't have a necklace, we thought we might as well add one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all the racket about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:26.17,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Saori Shirakawa (21)\NMisuzu's Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:23.45,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Why did you make them reject my successful audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Miss, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,One of the producers told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called them up and told them to fail me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saori auditioned for a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, your singing's terrible, and your acting also leaves a lot to be desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letting you perform in public would be embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't just decide that without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let you tarnish my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you were an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one even remembers Misuzu Shirakawa anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave her be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please escort our guests to the terrace, Yūka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like some jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To this day, Mother's very strict when it comes to acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mum's living in a dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a world where she is still a great actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to put it like that, Kyōsuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for that scene earlier, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letting you witness such an unseemly thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how old they get,\NI guess kids will always remain kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, children just don't know the extent of their parents' love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yūka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:23.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yūka Nakanishi (22)\NMaid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This isn't the rose jam we usually have, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:22.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:27.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was sure that there were still two jars left when I looked yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go and buy some right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother, don't get so angry about something like jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the set, people would never forget my favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a thing of the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies. I'll go get some immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kyōsuke, it's a bit early, but I shall take my medicine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get everything ready for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it's all a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Please excuse me for a moment while I go see how Yūka's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with this family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Chiharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She went to see how Yūka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, is Misuzu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} ill or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's just taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She takes a nap between 2 and 4 PM every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even takes sleeping pills, saying that it's good for her health and beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yūka! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault. I didn't look where I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I lurched to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is quite the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neesan{\r} staggered in front of the car and Yūka drove the car into the pond to avoid her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's not her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth is this commotion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me! I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it. I'm the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yūka, pack your bags and leave within the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally you'd ask whether anyone was hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car is insured and can be repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you always have to be so selfish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you ever think about someone else for a change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this how you should be talking to your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tired. I'm going back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Yūka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll talk to Mother later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, if you would, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All Dad did was step on the accelerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you smell something burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mistress's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misuzu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misuzu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kyōsuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, take that side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At around 2 PM today, the actress Misuzu Shirakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} passed away after a fire broke out in her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when you entered the room, Shirakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had already passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:41.75,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Detective Tamagawa (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She took sleeping pills before going to bed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and probably slept without noticing the fire, breathing in a large amount of smoke in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the fire sure broke out in an unusual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did your mother smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:11:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Not just her either, no one in this house smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:18.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means this is a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...was that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, since the day's almost over, and we can't be sure whether or not this was an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all we can do is head back to the station and wait for the forensic results.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Detective Tamagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be Sleeping Kogorō?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody! This fire was deliberately designed to kill Misuzu Shirakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying this was a murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's more, the killer is here in our midst.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Dad, at that time everyone was by the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. The fire was likely caused by a concentration of sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A concentration of sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a fire that occurs when something like water in a plastic bottle acts as a convex lens to concentrate and intensify sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that bundled sunlight was projected onto that picture, causing it to ignite, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this room faces north, so the sun doesn't shine in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please look out of the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That glass-sided building that looks like it was cut diagonally with a blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:13:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it remind you of anything, Kyōsuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we came to this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if that building reflected the sunlight it would merely hit the wall opposite the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, even if it was reflected by this mirror,\NI don't think the light would land on the portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainly seems impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bit higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then please turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light lands on the wall opposite the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, Yūka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please return the mirror that is lying on the floor to its original place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:13:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably fell in the commotion over putting out the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you see the little mark engraved on the pedestal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A similar one can also be found on the glass case,\Nso please place the mirror so the markings match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please adjust the angle of the mirror as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light falls onto the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do the same with the other two mirrors as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, this is what happened:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sunlight reflected off the glass-sided building,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,passed through the window, reflected off the full-length mirror on that wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then reflected once more off the three mirrors on the glass case,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before converging to one point on the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:15:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is likely that the killer meticulously planned the placement of the mirrors in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But please remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just before noon, I unintentionally toppled the mirrors when we were shown around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means, chances are that the position of the mirrors changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite this, the fire broke out according to the killer's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer returned the mirrors to their original positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct. And there is only one person who could have done so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who remained in this room while the rest of us went ahead to the terrace:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiharu Shirakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one but you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Chiharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You killed our mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mum only opened the window for two to three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:16:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could a fire even start in such a short time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you positioned the mirrors, you doused the painting with an inflammable chemical,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,likely the sort of diluent that is used when creating oil paintings, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Diluent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Volatile solutions like turpentine and petrol have a flash point of under 50° Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were also the one who hid the rose jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, Misuzu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sent Yūka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} off to buy new jam, giving you the opportunity to walk in front of her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What on earth is this commotion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.91,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with that car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.25,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can't you ever think about someone else for a change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:58.91,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is this how you should be talking to your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that what happened, Chiharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this true, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's your evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to accuse me like this, you better have some proof of what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Evidence, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. All this is nothing but speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does the fact that I was the last to leave this room prove that I repositioned the mirrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yūka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room is decorated with an arrangement of lilies, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the mistress liked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about the other rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. This is the only room with lilies in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am talking about evidence, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:18:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To put it simply, I'm talking about the lily pollen on the outside of your right sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What sort of evidence is that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would the pollen of a flower that can only be found in this room be on your right sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I touched the lilies with my arm at some point, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I'd remember something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lilies are in a vase on top of the glass case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the pollen is on the outside of your right sleeve,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that means that you faced the flowers and moved your right arm along the left side of the flowers in order to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, what was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:19:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the mirrors we used in the experiment earlier, which served to bundle the light by reflecting it, was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neesan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why did you kill her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman always called me "Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though she called you guys just "Kyōsuke" and "Saori".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of something like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father brought me into this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When my father decided to get married again with her, I was very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, she was a great actress who I admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I tried very hard to please her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't make any selfish requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I helped out around the house as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all I got in return from that woman was "Well done, Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}",
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Thank you, Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}", "That won't do, Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}", "Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}", "Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then last week...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:11.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, she doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's just a step-child after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:24.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, that's right. The only children through which the blood of Misuzu Shirakawa flows are Kyōsuke and Saori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:29.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She won't get a single yen of my fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is merely my personal opinion, but I think you tried too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A familial relationship isn't born from hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you {\i1}should{\i0} have been selfish from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You started the whole affair off on the wrong foot, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to the racetrack again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid! Of course I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. And you went and ate curry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do about dinner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's right there on your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A curry stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll admit that I had some curry, but that doesn't mean I went to the racetrack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. How did this get behind my ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange. Mysterious things do happen, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.47,0:23:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Know when to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your allowance will be cut by 50%!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have mercy! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:31.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're a detective! You should be paying attention to the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One knife thrust to the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two are the killers, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: The Figurine That Was Too Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.26,0:23:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Paint!
